    "title": [
      "Integrated SARS-CoV-2 serological and virological screening across an acute fever surveillance platform to monitor temporal changes in anti-spike antibody levels and risk of infection during sequential waves of variant transmission \u2014 Dominican Republic, March 2021 to August 2022"
